WEBVTT

26:34.280 --> 26:35.910 line:80%
What are you thinking?

26:37.480 --> 26:39.110 line:80%
Changning has always been in poor health

26:39.110 --> 26:40.300 line:80%
and is still taking medicine.

26:40.300 --> 26:42.760 line:80%
Where will you get the extra money
for his medicine?

26:42.760 --> 26:43.870 line:80%
Does that young man

26:44.150 --> 26:45.870 line:80%
have any family left?
